{"tid":804420,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"唉......今日返學比人串到喊=.=","createTime":"2018-09-03T04:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T04:14:25.000Z","uid":109983,"like":12,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3df32e10f37d5046df4b27e771cd875caa6a25d2","tid":804420,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"今日見d同學成班圍埋一齊講野,我想搭下嗲,點知佢地話我講野1999=.= <br />\r\n我話:你班傻的嗎仔緊係聽唔明我講乜啦,我智商300,所以你地同我溝通唔到姐 <br />\r\n然後其中一個同學聽到之後話: 哦...原來我地智商差成200咁多,唔怪之得啦... <br />\r\n咁我又接住講: 算啦,我都唔介意既...點知佢地竟然話我弱智仔, <br />\r\n仲同我講:我地呢度每個人既智商都係500以上,又叫我死開啦,白痴仔..咁＝︿＝ <br />\r\n聽到佢地咁講我忍唔住流左少少眼淚,然後跑走左,不過當時我仲係好型棍&gt;3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2dc9d0f1cbb80796e17fcb7e00c0fcc1e3bfae","tid":804420,"uid":189453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597707fecb816fe7d1d2cee328040a5c304b7fc8","tid":804420,"uid":170383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-10/10"},{"pid":"872359a7eb35fb24acd587c8df788ca2ce907dc1","tid":804420,"uid":139242,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"26b19de31a0c16ae7169bdef8bf237efaeaff70e","tid":804420,"uid":22947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"舊文翻炒"},{"pid":"a26be98c94573c96c11fb073b92afc6e0da917df","tid":804420,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T15:2